------------------------------------------------------------------------

# 7. What NOT to do

-   Do NOT compute entitlement in frontend
-   Do NOT infer billing status
-   Do NOT hardcode module access
-   Do NOT embed external services directly

------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Definition of Done

-   Every screen has an endpoint
-   Every endpoint returns explicit state
-   No UI assumptions required
-   Contract is stable and extendable
